@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #85386 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
The code is totally valid and also compiles fine on other targets. So I would say P-high because wasm32-unknown-unknown is tier 2
I wonder why declaring the proc_macros crate make the error disappear. I'm thinking to I-nominate this because it's specific to wasm target, we might need someone working specifically on this target

I'm still pretty new to all this and especially zulip but I can try to provide some context in the meeting. From what I have gathered the communication is text based? So it would be nice if you could ping me if I miss it
